{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"16":{"eng-name":"Sacrifice (Kitab Al-Dahaya)","ara-name":"كتاب الضحايا"}},"section_detail":{"16":{"hadithnumber_first":2788,"hadithnumber_last":2843,"arabicnumber_first":2788,"arabicnumber_last":2843}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":2793,"arabicnumber":2793,"text":"حَدَّثَنَا مُوسَى بْنُ إِسْمَاعِيلَ، حَدَّثَنَا وُهَيْبٌ، عَنْ أَيُّوبَ، عَنْ أَبِي قِلاَبَةَ، عَنْ أَنَسٍ، أَنَّ النَّبِيَّ صلى الله عليه وسلم نَحَرَ سَبْعَ بَدَنَاتٍ بِيَدِهِ قِيَامًا وَضَحَّى بِالْمَدِينَةِ بِكَبْشَيْنِ أَقْرَنَيْنِ أَمْلَحَيْنِ ‏.‏","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih Bukhari (1712)"}],"reference":{"book":16,"hadith":6},"chapter":{"id":4,"ara-name":"باب مَا يُسْتَحَبُّ مِنَ الضَّحَايَا","eng-name":"What Is Recommended Regarding Sacrifices","isFirstHadith":false}}]}